Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.21,0:00:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标已经确保了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 在明天早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您喝多了 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.13,0:00:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可不是你的房间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙是不是搞错了什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.49,0:00:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:00:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗 当然是正义的伙伴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别耍帅了 快放我下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你现在还是不要乱动比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Meister乙HiME啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是Meister乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯露
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后的总力战中幸免于难的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将过去穿越星辰 改造行星的多数技术封印
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把世界托付于 与主人共享生命的有着超常能力的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.40,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为秩序监视者的“乙HiME”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然经历了几度战乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多乙HiME与王失去了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:03:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 人们已将决定性的破灭留在了彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 希芙璐的爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在很远的地方 有很重要的工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈听我说 希芙璐长大之后呢 要成为乙HiME哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为乙HiME后帮助妈妈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同爸爸的份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 希芙璐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:03:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 希芙璐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐·弗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 叔叔因为生病所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介绍晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布鲁斯·瓦雷斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位是蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蕾娜·梦宫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你的叔叔是旧识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受他的请求来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说没想到会演变成和诱拐犯战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很少有如此暴力的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 只要我们来了你就没什么好担心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您救了我 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要谢的话谢她们就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾亚尔教团的修女·诗音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和她的乙HiME Meister拉凯露·真夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾亚尔教团?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不会对有难者视而不见的团体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在谈了你的事后说是会帮我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们教团是绝对不会对迷途的羔羊坐视不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是想要捐款的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说拉凯露!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真正的Meister乙HiME吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被真正的Meister乙HiME救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痒~~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你们就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温特布鲁姆王国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叔叔在那里等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.69,0:06:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔他?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 能见到叔叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙拿行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister羌德拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天真是帮大忙了 艾里奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然能在这里见到身为五柱的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为追查西巴鲁兹是我的工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份谢礼下次我会好好还的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢礼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 下次回到温特之后再联络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:06:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是我力所能及的事都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.24,0:07:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下 艾里奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我已经忍不住了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你和毕业之前完全没变嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是你自己说什么都行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和那是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们已经半年没见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是什么啊 我们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.42,*Note,NTP,0,0,0,,注:仆たち通常指一男一女 女生间应该是私たち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 蕾娜好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到有趣的东西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙HiME啊 那些传言也是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 像这么热情的都快成十八禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么那么 拉凯露小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 诗音酱吃醋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你说什么蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:08:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 教团不是会鞭打同性恋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要说的那么直白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗音酱 鞭打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞭打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在的话就快来救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在晚饭前我会来叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你自身安全 不要出房间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 所以说了不能开窗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:08:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是尼娜它…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 保安会马上帮忙抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点而已也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你这样很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐 连衣裙做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.08,0:09:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 希芙璐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是对得起对不起的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐可真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然干出那么危险的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是昨天被诱拐的女孩应该做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜小姐请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 连那里也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂停 暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 那孩子也很高兴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没被这么训斥了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我 蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然乙HiME就是厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你刻意隐藏也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那么厉害的事就只有乙HiME能办到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和Meister艾里奥特和拉凯露是同级生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然主人就是布鲁斯先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没能成为乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.62,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在毕业时害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 蕾娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想成为乙HiME哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在面试时落榜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的母亲曾经反对我成为乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐 你认为乙HiME是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么正式地问我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙HiME就是暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是非常大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在加尔德罗贝上课我很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也交了很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我没有使用那力量的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲她也一定是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 放弃了当乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和母亲怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有见面 因为有许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很难回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闹过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 因为我也听说了希芙璐小姐的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有了像希芙璐小姐这样的后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乙HiME也并不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.61,0:12:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯大人 发现目标了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么 不会错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有数个阿斯瓦德的生化人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颇有组织规模的在行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾里奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个女孩落入西巴鲁兹手里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持现在的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们真祖大人的乙HiME的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是… 在她的身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己要对自己的任务抱有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河之蓝玉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是夏姆洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下令C5开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我还不习惯这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就得好好享受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请伸出手 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主险些就被击沉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人一眼就看穿的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能被骗啊 希芙璐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.44,0:15:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊 艾里酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 艾里奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脸色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 好 去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我肚子都咕咕叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴兽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这里使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位乙HiME 这里就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了 拉凯露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.65,0:16:01.82,*Materialise,NTP,0,0,0,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&H7B1FDE&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.08,*Materialise,NTP,0,0,0,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&HB9813A&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息下吧 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种程度的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉凯露她们马上就能轰走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但和蕾娜在一起却真的感觉会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐的性格太过少女向了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和母亲和好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人去觉得为难的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我陪你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这时太放松了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜总散发着一种让人放不下心的感觉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我妈妈稍稍有些像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.93,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包围了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次 是将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有赤之刃的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以吾之名将你那力量解放
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:36.37,*Materialise,NTP,0,0,0,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&H7667F9&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤高的红翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蕾娜·赛亚兹么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在发什么呆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不快攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.19,0:19:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 不胜惶恐 请你们忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分神的话就会死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.38,0:19:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 愕天王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大被…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉德大人 奴兽因为害怕而不受控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就先饶了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希芙璐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都别动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁斯·温特布鲁姆殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰·史密斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有些仓促 不过就让你们看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“编织者”的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.42,0:20:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 M-9
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.93,0:21:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.78,0:21:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,良好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 有任务
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去排除你面前的红色乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布鲁斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看吧希芙璐·弗兰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加尔德罗贝建校以来的怪物动真格是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Meister GEM也不行吗 蕾娜酱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜酱的力量太过强大
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也控制不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 那可是温特王室的守护石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.36,0:22:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个女孩落入西巴鲁兹手里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾里奥特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:47.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾里奥特 你这是做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.35,0:23:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
